data(package = "fivethirtyeight")

For this assignment, Ill be using the dataset titled bad_drivers. The dataset contains statistics about the degree to which certain types of fatal collisions occur by state.

Reference link with additional background: https://fivethirtyeight.com/features/which-state-has-the-worst-drivers/
